求五大訴求，缺一不可。唔好再放任何人上枱，要放就放「香港人」三個字"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T09:46:46.000Z","msg":"只係針對返「平凡父婦」嘅信<br />\n佢地都唔可以代表到所有佢個輩嘅人<br />\n大家都好清楚有好多老一輩嘅人係支持緊年輕人<br />\n所以呢封信目的係抵消返個封信嘅觀點同感覺<br />\n呢封信唔係要代表所有香港人<br />\n而係令大家支持後生一輩"},{"pid":"ccb2a8f259cfa6132928fac8f7f0d01d41846399","tid":1432563,"uid":237691,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T09:50:48.000Z","msg":"喊咗"},{"pid":"753c73c8c1cd4fa9b073884da57bf830f256f948","tid":1432563,"uid":295639,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T09:51:07.000Z","msg":"&quot;我們不只是勇武抗爭，而是與和理非一體兩面&quot;<br />\n不能同事更多 衷心支持"},{"pid":"fb33f5b43e0065756f569edfe68d48a8df0e52eb","tid":1432563,"uid":167634,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ccb2a8f259cfa6132928fac8f7f0d01d41846399","tid":1432563,"uid":237691,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T09:50:48.000Z","msg":"喊咗"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T09:51:24.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fec538c99150351aa79138365f6a49342c327c38","tid":1432563,"uid":295639,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ccb2a8f259cfa6132928fac8f7f0d01d41846399","tid":1432563,"uid":237691,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T09:50:48.000Z","msg":"喊咗"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T09:51:46.000Z","msg":"我日日都喊 撐住"},{"pid":"f0f5e7ce46eb0aeaff712f5f862731861ee37895","tid":1432563,"uid":237691,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fec538c99150351aa79138365f6a49342c327c38","tid":1432563,"uid":295639,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ccb2a8f259cfa6132928fac8f7f0d01d41846399","tid":1432563,"uid":237691,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"